{"tid":999543,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【校園欺凌】第3條欺凌片流出！董之英中學1男生被同學蒙頭壓騎","createTime":"2019-01-28T19:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T00:51:31.000Z","uid":160807,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea2c2015d8b02ce2e179454508c6e1dc9d27fb1","tid":999543,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190128/large/1548682466_919a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190128%2Flarge%2F1548682466_919a.png&h=b2359790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n馬鞍山仁濟醫院董之英紀念中學集體欺凌醜聞越揭越多，繼有2名學生遭校內惡霸剝褲打屁股及重拳槌背後，今午（28日）亦流出第3條懷疑集體欺凌影片。facebook專頁「馬鞍山之友MOSers（Since 2014）」今午以「代Post、董之英Again」為題，公佈涉事影片。雖然短片只有6秒長，但清楚見到1名男學生，遭多名男學生圍住，並有同學騎在他身上，使其趴在地上，無法動彈。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑施虐的同學見狀，未有罷休，反而用毛衣，強行蒙住該男學生頭部。該男學生其後撥開毛衣，並以手遮臉。其間有人曾大叫「唔好打！」以及「無X玩！」此外，片段亦有後製「Bully（欺凌）」一字。<br />\n<br />\n公佈首條董之英中學集體欺凌醜聞影片的葉先生表示，該片段由1位現時仍在董之英中學內就讀的學生轉交給他，現時已在舊生之間流傳。不過，他未有透露更多資料。《蘋果》已向校方查詢，正等待回覆。教育局回覆指，已派員到有關學校了解，重申局方「零容忍」校園欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190128/59196343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190128%2F59196343&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a3e8c2fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190128%2F59196343&h=b39127fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190128/59196343</a>"},{"pid":"f94bdf71c685bed739fef6f5435cf189bf273e45","tid":999543,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T19:34:44.000Z","msg":"天將降大任於斯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b2c49f638e7d07eb7ab5728c8373230fee713e","tid":999543,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbb4ec994f03e00c134b0b94b22ece0a14668b6","tid":999543,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}